OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FJersey's Government has announced
OL,7,Fmajor changes to who can apply for
OL,8,Fsocial housing.
OL,10,FKey changes were unveiled by the
OL,11,Fisland's Housing Minister, Deputy Sam
OL,12,FMezec on Friday 19 December.
OL,14,FThe reforms, which form part of an
OL,15,Fupdate to the original roadmap
OL,16,Fpublished in 2023, mean more islanders
OL,17,Fcan apply for subsidised housing,
OL,18,Fopening access to those who do not
OL,19,Fcurrently meet the priority criteria.
