OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FThe changes come as more than 600
OL,7,Fhouseholds are currently on the
OL,8,FAffordable Housing Gateway waiting
OL,9,Flist.
OL,11,FThe updated roadmap includes:
OL,13,F"Not only have we made significant
OL,14,Fprogress against the previous roadmap,
OL,15,Fbut there is a growing supply of new
OL,16,Fhomes to meet demand," the Housing
OL,17,FMinister told ITV News.
