OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,F"Now is the time to further improve
OL,7,Fopportunities for those looking for
OL,8,Faffordable, good-quality homes,
OL,9,Fparticularly for younger Islanders who
OL,10,Fmay not see a future in Jersey.
OL,12,F"Introducing a general needs band will
OL,13,Fopen the door to more Islanders,
OL,14,Fensuring that younger adults and
OL,15,Fhouseholds who do not meet existing
OL,16,Fpriority criteria can benefit from the
OL,17,Fstability and affordability of social
OL,18,Fhousing."
