OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FThe roadmap includes several other
OL,7,Fchanges, including an annual review of
OL,8,Fincome thresholds to ensure they
OL,9,Fremain aligned with affordability and
OL,10,Fcost-of-living changes.
OL,12,FThere will also be quarterly reviews
OL,13,Fof long-standing applications to
OL,14,F"ensure timely allocation" and
OL,15,F"identify barriers to accessing
OL,16,Fhousing", alongside a "targeted
OL,17,Freview" of Band 1 prioritisation.
