OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FThe Housing Minister says that those
OL,7,Fat risk of homelessness or urgent
OL,8,Fhousing needs would "remain the
OL,9,Fhighest priority" for social rented
OL,10,Fhousing.
OL,12,FIn 2024, the Housing Minister widened
OL,13,Faccess to social housing for islanders
OL,14,Faged 25 and over who do not have
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FDeputy Hilary Jeune, who chairs the
OL,18,Fyouth homelessness charity Jersey
OL,19,FAssociation of Youth and Friendship
OL,20,F(JAYF), welcomes the announcement.
