OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,F"Every day, we hear from youngsters
OL,7,Fthat the cost of living in Jersey is
OL,8,Freally related to housing, and that's
OL,9,Fa big problem. Lots of youngsters want
OL,10,Fto leave the island."
OL,12,FThe Deputy added that she doesn't
OL,13,Fbelieve the new changes will increase
OL,14,Fpressure on social housing providers
OL,15,Flike Andium.
