OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,F"Andium has built a lot of one and two-
OL,7,Fbedroom flats recently. There's more
OL,8,Fcoming on the market and coming into
OL,9,Ftheir possession in the coming months,
OL,10,Fand those can be used to help this
OL,11,Freduction in the age group to 18.
OL,13,F"There are also a lot of family homes
OL,14,Fbeing built at the moment, meaning
OL,15,Fmore families can move out of homes
OL,16,Fthat are not right for them".
