OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FDeputy Jeune added that young people
OL,7,Fstruggling to pay their rent can
OL,8,Faccess income support from the
OL,9,Fisland's government, as well as
OL,10,Fsupport from JAYF.
OL,12,FKate Wright, CEO of Jersey domestic
OL,13,Fabuse charity FREEDA, told ITV News
OL,14,Fthe changes are going to have a "life-
OL,15,Fchanging impact" on women's lives.
OL,17,FIndividuals with 'Entitled'
OL,18,Fresidential status who have lived in
OL,19,FJersey for less than ten years are
OL,20,Fcurrently unable to access social
OL,21,Fhousing.
