OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FIt currently means that victims of
OL,7,Fdomestic abusers who have lived in the
OL,8,Fisland for less time may feel
OL,9,Fpressured to stay with their abuser to
OL,10,Favoid becoming homeless.
OL,12,F"It means (victims) are left with the
OL,13,Fterrible choice to either return to
OL,14,Ftheir perpetrator with their children
OL,15,For if they're here on a spousal visa -
OL,16,Fto potentially leave the island," Ms
OL,17,FWright explained.
