OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FUnder the new changes, this
OL,7,Frestriction will be removed, allowing
OL,8,Fall Entitled individuals to be
OL,9,Feligible if they satisfy all other
OL,10,Fcriteria.
OL,12,F"One of the greatest barriers a lot of
OL,13,Fwomen face is access to social
OL,14,Fhousing, so removing that barrier
OL,15,Fremoves the biggest barrier for women
OL,16,Fescaping their abuser."
