OL,3,CIsland social housing eligibility
OL,4,Cwidened to tackle soaring rent costs
OL,6,FMs Wright believes it's a much more
OL,7,F"humane approach" to supporting
OL,8,Fvulnerable people on the island who
OL,9,Fare not necessarily Jersey-born and
OL,10,Fhaven't lived on the island for more
OL,11,Fthan ten years.
OL,13,F"It's about looking at their lives and
OL,14,Fnot just how long they've lived on the
OL,15,Fisland."
